e stacktrace:\r\nhttps://wiki.ubuntu.com/DebuggingProgramCrash", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Ubuntu has a tool to provide useful information about a crash, it is called apport: <a href=\"https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Apport\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Apport</a></p>\n<p>Seems like it does not need any special configuration for our part, but this needs to be confirmed:\n<a href=\"https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Apport/DeveloperHowTo\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Apport/DeveloperHowTo</a></p>\n<p>And it can provide an easy way to ask for the stacktrace:\n<a href=\"https://wiki.ubuntu.com/DebuggingProgramCrash\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://wiki.ubuntu.com/DebuggingProgramCrash</a></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Jose Luis Rivero", "uuid": "{d12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/109284c8b83411dbc7492138f6167e9ed=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsJR-5.png"}}, "nickname": "Jose Luis Rivero", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:155a32e2-420c-4d50-98e0-0e722f63f906"}, "state": "wontfix", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2012-12-18T03:54:05.115783+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2013-08-06T11:25:30.643795+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 16}